data.description: Huge price reduction !!!  Introducing this stunning colonial-style home in Collington Estates! This property offers more space inside than meets the eye, providing ample room for comfortable living. Step inside and be captivated by the dramatic two-story family room featuring a magnificent fireplace trim that extends to the ceiling. This impressive centerpiece creates a cozy and inviting atmosphere for gatherings with family and friends. The granite countertop in the kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with sleek black appliances. The eat-in kitchen area is perfect for casual dining, while the hardwood floors in the foyer, kitchen, and family room add a touch of elegance. A full bath on the lower level and space for additional bedrooms adds convenience and flexibility. You will also find a convenient first-floor library on the main level, ideal for a home office, study, or extra bedroom. Additionally, the basement features a recreation room or theater room, allowing you to enjoy movie nights in the comfort of your home. Enjoy outdoor living and entertaining on the deck off the breakfast area, perfect for morning coffee or evening barbecues. The patio extends to the rear yard, providing additional space for relaxation and outdoor activities. The basement offers extra storage space, a cedar closet, and room for expansion, allowing you to customize the home to your needs and preferences. Take advantage of this opportunity to own a beautiful colonial-style home in Collington Estates with exceptional features. Schedule a showing today and envision yourself living in this remarkable property in a much-desired enclave!
